{"tid":1804000,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（Make Hong Kong Great Again）良心生活圈 by 龍門老細","createTime":"2019-12-30T15:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:29.000Z","uid":18245,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0acf9eaee2f500994cf3edefd57057ac2f812a2b","tid":1804000,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S8zxw2c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS8zxw2c.png&h=ee99670c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃店回饋運動</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參考老細嘅睇法，成立良心生活圈，同時support各行業嘅手足同振興本土文化。<br />\n<br />\n<code>「點解會有黃店？因為你撐年輕人、撐抗爭者；好嘞，當你係黃店，賺多咗錢嘞，係咪應該要諗吓，點樣用返賺多咗嘅錢去幫呢班年輕人？你賺多咗嘅錢，唔好袋晒，袋一半吖，拎一半出嚟幫年輕人。\n</code><br />\n<br />\n<code>「如果你係黃店，我原本賺100萬一個月，而家賺120萬一個月，我袋晒落褲袋，咁唔係『黃色經濟圈』囉！講得衰啲就係食人血饅頭，或者係，好經濟囉！」</code><br />\n<br />\n如果我哋每人拎啲賺多咗嘅錢出嚟，成立一個基金去幫助我哋想幫嘅人，照顧義士同佢哋嘅家人，甚至用呢筆錢拎<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">成立一個功能上類似政府</span></strong></span>嘅組織去look after 自己人同用作長期抗爭嘅時候，距離真係光復香港就唔遠啦。<br />\n<br />\n詳情可以睇下邊2條link<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">【抗暴之戰】嫌「黃色經濟圈」改壞名太市儈 龍門老闆寄語黃店回饋運動：唔好對唔住黃！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9q00UVXMRg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dc9q00UVXMRg&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=f14b9a44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c9q00UVXMRg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 《香港人抗爭的日與夜》集會 set咗時間 一開就係良心生活圈個part</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QYx74uOmOG0?t=5279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQYx74uOmOG0%3Ft%3D5279&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=6b114cd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QYx74uOmOG0?t=5279</a><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好忘記每一步都係用血同淚換返嚟<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/WellinformedComposedFattaileddunnart-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FWellinformedComposedFattaileddunnart-size_restricted.gif&h=54189c8c&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"c1295aebfcd7edd7eae2b2d46fbdf3c8a1e0d47e","tid":1804000,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=5e0d67e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=05fb37a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要29000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1803675</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJnaXPXn3VG1rMaGvML0ROe4%3D&h=708ba389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a><br />\n<br /